Two Javascript snippets to generate a future date for a given weekday calculated off current date


banner_content.html

This code goes into Content of Banner and will generate a future date 7 days from date now.
Ideal for end dates of sales



banner_new.phtml

This adds a backgrounded text message which provides the opportunity for displaying 
the date of the next upcoming Sunday, based on the current date.

Add this code to new.phtml from about line 31
/home/USER/public_html/app/design/frontend/PACKAGE/THEME/template/catalog/product/new.phtml
and you can use it as part of a message with an end date for new products on sale at the top of new.phtml
Add it undeneath a banner and can be matched in background colour to appear as part of the banner.
Refresh cache to ensure changes are visible
